1. When hovering over an element, only the **element itself should rotate**. The **chain/rope attached to it should remain fixed** and must not rotate.

2. When dragging the element around, the **chain/rope must stay anchored to its original base point**. It should stretch naturally from that fixed point to the element, similar to an **elastic rope tied to a fixed place with a element attached at the other end**. The base point should never move.